				Functions
					Function: GetSwitchFields
						Description:
						Returns
							Boolean:
						Parameters
							Receive Number: nNewSwitchNo
							Receive Number: nNewSwitchChannelNo
							Receive String: sNewSwitchDesc
							Receive String: sNewSwitchStatus
						Static Variables
						Local variables
						Actions
							Set nNewSwitchNo = nSwitchNo
							Set nNewSwitchChannelNo = nSwitchChannelNo
							Set sNewSwitchDesc = sSwitchDesc
							Set sNewSwitchStatus = sSwitchStatus
							Return TRUE
					Function: SetSwitchFields
						Description:
