		                 Description: 
		                 Named Menus 
		                 Menu 
			                 Popup Menu: Table Actions
				                 Enabled when: 
				                 Status Text: 
				                 Menu Item Name: 
				                 Menu Item: Add Row
					                 Keyboard Accelerator: (none)
					                 Status Text: 
